column2: SELECT SpecObjId, z, ra, dec, spectroFlux_u, spectroFlux_g, spectroFlux_r, spectroFlux_i, spectroFlux_z FROM SpecObjAll s1 WHERE class = &&& AND zWarning = # AND exists (SELECT z FROM SpecObjAll s2 WHERE class = &&& AND zWarning = # and  s1.z = s2.z GROUP BY z HAVING count(*) >= #) ORDER BY z
